{"lastModified":1772145165422,"uri":"c::51632648983::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Bahamas\n\nAtlantia is a 67’ overall length power catamaran with a 33-foot beam. She features six staterooms and six bathrooms, plus crew quarters, accommodating up to 12 guests overnight and up to 12 guests on day charters. This gorgeous catamaran provides a smooth ride for an unforgettable charter experience.\n\nAtlantia boasts a spacious, fully equipped galley with a large island, industrial dishwasher, full-size range and oven with an enhanced hood, and a double-bay sink. The salon features a large retractable TV and a lounge/dining area with two convertible tables. Spacious all-teak decks and lounge areas on the bow and stern provide ample room to relax. Outdoor amenities include two refrigerators, sinks, and an ice maker, while the helm is equipped with state-of-the-art navigation technology—making Atlantia the perfect yacht for entertaining on the water.\n","blueprint":{"name":"ATLANTIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44d9b070-11c6-11f1-bbe5-6316c49d3624/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44edada0-11c6-11f1-bbe5-6316c49d3624/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44da25a0-11c6-11f1-be4d-69048a3b2075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44e940d0-11c6-11f1-bbe5-6316c49d3624/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44ebd8e1-11c6-11f1-bbe5-6316c49d3624/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44ebd8e0-11c6-11f1-bbe5-6316c49d3624/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::437e1f70-11c3-11f1-9865-a73622f46bb4::assets::44eb63b0-11c6-11f1-bbe5-6316c49d3624/{ima